# AI Agentic System - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and add your actual keys

# ============================================================================
# LLM API KEYS (At least one required)
# ============================================================================

# Google Gemini (Recommended - Default)
# Get your key at: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here

# OpenAI (Optional)
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Anthropic Claude (Optional)
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here

# ============================================================================
# GMAIL API CONFIGURATION (Optional - Required for email sending feature)
# ============================================================================

# Email sending now uses Gmail API with OAuth2 for better security
# No need to store passwords in .env!
# 
# Setup steps:
# 1. Download credentials.json from Google Cloud Console
# 2. Place it in the project root directory
# 3. Run: python test_gmail_oauth.py
# 4. Authorize in the browser that opens
# 5. token.json will be created automatically
#
# See README.md for detailed setup instructions
